OL,6,FWarning: The following article
OL,7,Fcontains references to anorexia and
OL,8,Feating disorders
OL,10,FA former patient at Ty Llidiard, the
OL,11,Fchildren's mental health hospital in
OL,12,FBridgend, is helping the previously
OL,13,Ftroubled in-patient unit to turn its
OL,14,Ffortunes around.
OL,16,FHelen, 22, from Cardiff, is combining
OL,17,Fher studies to become a doctor with
OL,18,Fimproving patient safety and standards
OL,19,Fat Ty Llidiard.
