OL,6,FThe year 2020 was a difficult time for
OL,7,Fmany, and that was when Helen arrived
OL,8,Fat Ty Llidiard to begin her treatment
OL,9,Ffor anorexia.
OL,11,FShe studied for her A-Levels there at
OL,12,Fwhat was an unhappy time for herself,
OL,13,Fpersonally, and for the unit in
OL,14,Fgeneral.
OL,16,FHelen said: "I wasn't really engaging,
OL,17,FI wasn't there to get better. At that
OL,18,Fpoint, I just thought, 'I'm going to
OL,19,Feat my way out - I just want to get
OL,20,Fout of here, I don't want to be here.'
