OL,6,F"It was very regimented, very
OL,7,Fpaternalistic - you did what you were
OL,8,Ftold. There were no sorts of
OL,9,Factivities - there was nothing to do
OL,10,Fat all. We would just sit in the
OL,11,Fcorridors and you'd be dwelling on the
OL,12,Ffact that you were there while
OL,13,Feveryone else was getting on with
OL,14,Ftheir life."
OL,16,FTy Llidiard is one of only two highly
OL,17,Fspecialist CAMHS (Child and Adolescent
OL,18,FMental Health Services) units in
OL,19,FWales. Historically, however, it
OL,20,Fhasn't been without its issues.
