OL,6,FA 16-year-old patient died there in
OL,7,F2018, which led to Cwm Taf Morgannwg -
OL,8,Fthe health board which runs the #15m
OL,9,Fpurpose-built unit - being issued with
OL,10,Fa prevention of future deaths report.
OL,12,FSerious concerns were also raised
OL,13,Fabout leadership and culture at the
OL,14,Funit. So much so that, in November
OL,15,F2021, it was escalated to the highest
OL,16,Flevel of enhanced monitoring by the
OL,17,FWelsh Health Specialised Services
OL,18,FCommittee (WHSSC).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
