OL,4,Cold unit on its own path to recovery
OL,6,FHelen said: "Not many people
OL,7,Funderstand what it's like to be at Ty
OL,8,FLlidiard unless you've been there
OL,9,Fyourself. I'm not there to tell nurses
OL,10,Fhow to be nurses, but I can explain
OL,11,Fwhat it's like to have an eating
OL,12,Fdisorder.
OL,14,F"It's trying to combine those two
OL,15,Fareas of expertise to make that well-
OL,16,Frounded, holistic approach."
OL,18,FThe improvement strategy for the unit
OL,19,Fis underpinned by the "Four Cs" of
OL,20,Fbeing caring, calm, compassionate and
OL,21,Fconfident.
