OL,6,FFor Lloyd Griffiths, Cwm Taf
OL,7,FMorgannwg's Head of Mental Health
OL,8,FNursing, listening to the patient's
OL,9,Fvoice is an integral part of
OL,10,Fspearheading change and creating a
OL,11,Fbetter environment for all at Ty
OL,12,FLlidiard.
OL,14,FMr Griffiths said: "We're now trying
OL,15,Fto involve the young people and their
OL,16,Ffamilies in as much of the work we do,
OL,17,Fboth clinically and on the improvement
OL,18,Fside.
