OL,6,FShe added: "It's never going to be
OL,7,Feasy for anyone to be at Ty Llidiard -
OL,8,Fit's not a holiday camp, by any means
OL,9,F- but just making that really
OL,10,Fdifficult time a bit nicer (for
OL,11,Fpatients) and seeing that come to life
OL,12,Fis really, really lovely."
